value.value: Adult motor neuron (Takemura et al., 2023; Marin et al., 2024). It is a secondary neuron (Takemura et al., 2023; Marin et al., 2024). It exits the VNC via the first abdominal nerve (Takemura et al., 2023; Marin et al., 2024). It receives input in the T3 leg neuropil and sends output to the metathoracic leg (Takemura et al., 2023; Marin et al., 2024). Its predicted neurotransmitter is glutamate (Eckstein et al., 2024). There are approximately 2 of these cells per organism and their somas are found in the metathoracic neuromere (Takemura et al., 2023; Marin et al., 2024).

value.value: Adult chemosensory ascending neuron that innervates a taste bristle (Takemura et al., 2023; Marin et al., 2024). It enters the VNC via the abdominal nerve (Takemura et al., 2023; Marin et al., 2024). It receives input in the abdomen (Takemura et al., 2023; Marin et al., 2024). Its predicted neurotransmitter is acetylcholine (Eckstein et al., 2024). There are approximately 36 of these cells per organism (Takemura et al., 2023; Marin et al., 2024).

value.value: Adult proprioceptive sensory neuron (Takemura et al., 2023; Marin et al., 2024). It enters the VNC via the dorsal metathoracic nerve (Takemura et al., 2023; Marin et al., 2024). It receives input in the haltere and sends output to multiple regions (Takemura et al., 2023; Marin et al., 2024). Its predicted neurotransmitter is acetylcholine (Eckstein et al., 2024). There are approximately 2 of these cells per organism (Takemura et al., 2023; Marin et al., 2024).

value.value: Adult proprioceptive sensory neuron (Takemura et al., 2023; Marin et al., 2024). It enters the VNC via the posterior dorsal mesothoracic nerve (Takemura et al., 2023; Marin et al., 2024). It receives input in the thoracic tergum and sends output to the haltere neuropil and wing neuropil (Takemura et al., 2023; Marin et al., 2024). Its predicted neurotransmitter is acetylcholine (Eckstein et al., 2024). There are approximately 2 of these cells per organism (Takemura et al., 2023; Marin et al., 2024).
